{"tid":275432,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"涉聘中國人來港行乞　3港人被捕","createTime":"2017-06-08T04:33:21.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-09T02:35:29.000Z","uid":20933,"like":24,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"119fd7cbe4672d3a4cb3016d4c2eeb52fae4687d","tid":275432,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T04:33:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170131/large/1485831833_9a90.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170131%2Flarge%2F1485831833_9a90.jpg&h=d30d59fe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n東九龍總區機動部隊人員聯同觀塘、黃大仙、秀茂坪警區人員、入境事務處及勞工處，根據線報及經深入調查後，昨日凌晨約5時進行代號為「冠軍」(CHAMPION)的行動，於觀塘、黃大仙及秀茂坪區，拘捕10男8女，年齡介乎24至69歲，當中包括13名持雙程證內地人、3名本地人及兩名非華裔人士。<br />\n<br />\n當中的三名本地人，涉嫌協助及教唆他人非法入境、僱用非法勞工及行乞被捕，後獲准保釋候查。其餘被捕人士現正被扣留調查。部分被捕人士稍後將交入境事務處跟進。<br />\n<br />\n近年香港街頭湧現不少乞丐，當中包括傷殘人士。《蘋果》曾追蹤有關人士，發現他們有部分是來自內地一慈善團體，被指為賺快錢獲安港來港賣唱行乞( <a href=\"http://bit.ly/2nTV9RS\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2nTV9RS&d=Cw2PUvMBpwLuQPtG7jJqAjOU%2Fspzl0GStOx2So8CiJ8%3D&h=ba14c6d8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2nTV9RS</a> )。"},{"pid":"d4f38ff81a6d7ba24e73cf8bb43813f1c1c7dac8","tid":275432,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T04:34:31.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?issue=20170608&amp;guid=56798929&amp;category_guid=10829391&amp;category=instant\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fissue%3D20170608%26guid%3D56798929%26category_guid%3D10829391%26category%3Dinstant&d=Cw2PUvMBpwLuQPtG7jJqAjOU%2Fspzl0GStOx2So8CiJ8%3D&h=78e8e1a2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fissue%3D20170608%26guid%3D56798929%26category_guid%3D10829391%26category%3Dinstant&h=41ce6b59\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?issue=20170608&amp;guid=56798929&amp;category_guid=10829391&amp;category=instant</a>"},{"pid":"ef357bd3ae109e07148fb76bea3911032a5d3d2d","tid":275432,"uid":25858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T04:41:47.000Z","msg":"本地人都係新移民<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ff9a540311875fe38c157aca19d75207350ef31","tid":275432,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T06:30:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c32f7cfaa7059e2ca7d374ad2e190113d34116ba","tid":275432,"uid":77196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T06:33:11.000Z","msg":"呢張圖真係應景 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"14c2204fa95f60f3629648c163d4212278984c08","tid":275432,"uid":30487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T06:35:26.000Z","msg":"跟特首對著幹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"38cf55f058d4a44e391212030bc23db6cc3f7317","tid":275432,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T09:00:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d20b49c7c07a6c077f7df007f31725d96e03d477","tid":275432,"uid":50740,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T12:57:20.000Z","msg":"拉紅褸個阿姑啦"},{"pid":"1fa6c3003e82492dc0e1a533aa370738df14281f","tid":275432,"uid":53186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T15:41:29.000Z","msg":"仲有蝻"},{"pid":"b40f8a0794b94f96c3265f266234228b31c5a78d","tid":275432,"uid":53186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T15:41:41.000Z","msg":"仲有蝻"},{"pid":"3cb48e0f12493fbaa562b5f9e7a7983b5f1ba4bc","tid":275432,"uid":53186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T15:42:07.000Z","msg":"仲有蝻"},{"pid":"f2aac83ed2654db73a3775a2794cd0df1f7fff4b","tid":275432,"uid":20933,"like":0,"d